data.title: Foreign Currency Exchange Services
data.meta_description: Save time and effort by pre-ordering foreign currency at any Huntington branch. Click to learn more about how Huntington handles foreign currency.
data.text:
Traveling for business or pleasure? Huntington customers can save time by ordering foreign currency before a trip. You might even save money compared to airport exchange services.

Visit any Huntington branch to order from more than 75 world currencies. Enjoy the convenience of getting the local currency before you travel:

$15 flat fee for each foreign currency order and redemption at a Huntington branch ‡

Foreign coin may not be purchased or redeemed

No minimum amount; up to $20,000 in currency exchange

Save time once you arrive at your destination

Exchange foreign currency when you return for $15 flat fee per order‡

Visit any Huntington branch before your next trip.
